<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f0f8ff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .app-card {
            background: #f0f8ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 100px;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .app-content {
            flex: 3;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .app-content h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
        .app-content p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .app-content ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .app-content li {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .app-content .section-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Sneak Peak into My Life</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <% const content = [
            { 
                title: "My Education", 
                description: `
                    As a Computer Science student at Purdue University, I am actively involved in a variety of organizations and labs. My academic journey is shaped by a commitment to excellence and a passion for innovation. Here are some highlights:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>IDEAS Lab</strong>: Engaging in cutting-edge research and innovative projects.</li>
                        <li><strong>Purdue Fusion Studio for Engineering and Entertainment</strong>: Collaborating on interdisciplinary projects that merge technology and creativity.</li>
                        <li><strong>Director of CAST at Anvil</strong>: Leading and organizing events to foster a culture of creativity and innovation.</li>
                        <li><strong>Project Manager at ML@Purdue</strong>: Overseeing machine learning projects and guiding teams towards successful outcomes.</li>
                        <li><strong>Technical Assistant at GDSC</strong>: Providing technical support and resources to enhance student learning.</li>
                        <li><strong>Former Vice President of the Phoenix Club</strong>: Leading initiatives and activities that promote student engagement and leadership.</li>
                    </ul>
                ` 
            },
            { 
                title: "Some Things I Enjoy", 
                description: `
                    Life is not just about work; it's also about the experiences that bring joy and fulfillment. Here are some of my favorite activities:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Folding Intricate Origami Dragons</strong>: A relaxing and creative hobby that sharpens focus and patience.</li>
                        <li><strong>Taking Long Walks in the Park</strong>: Enjoying nature and finding peace in the tranquility of the outdoors.</li>
                        <li><strong>Snowboarding</strong>: The thrill and exhilaration of carving through fresh snow on the slopes.</li>
                        <li><strong>Watching Sunsets</strong>: Captivated by the brilliant colors that paint the sky during the golden hour.</li>
                        <li><strong>Playing Basketball</strong>: Enjoying the competitive spirit and teamwork involved in the game.</li>
                    </ul>
                ` 
            },
            { 
                title: "What I Love Working On", 
                description: `
                    I am driven by the ambition to build the next big thing, focusing on creating impactful innovations that people genuinely want to use. My professional interests include:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Building Cool Innovations</strong>: Developing technology that makes a clear and positive difference in people's lives.</li>
                        <li><strong>Making a Positive Impact</strong>: Ensuring that my work contributes to the betterment of society.</li>
                        <li><strong>Pushing Boundaries</strong>: Continuously exploring new ideas and pushing the limits of what's possible.</li>
                    </ul>
                    By combining my educational background, personal interests, and professional ambitions, I strive to create a well-rounded and fulfilling life.
                ` 
            },
        ]; %>

        <% content.forEach(section => { %>
            <div class="app-card">
                <div class="app-content">
                    <h2><%= section.title %></h2>
                    <p><%- section.description %></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        <% }) %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
